{
  "stem": "24885.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was all it was in Radom, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, there were quite a few thousand people-- maybe 4,000 or 5,000 because it was the main ammunition factory that supplied.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But like I said, like everybody else knew the war was lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew everything coming back from the Russian front and the Russians were not too far from us anymore, in Lublin or so.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They couldn't even get a train for us so they marched us for thee days to a city called Tomaszow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, anybody who couldn't walk anymore was put on a wagon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took him to the forest and shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We heard the shots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't see it, but we knew-- people that I knew from home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, I can give you names of some of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We came into a-- but they told us that we're going to work in a factory near, near Stuttgart or so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we figured that the officers of the camp and so on are trying to hide their own skin that they don't have to go into the Russian front, and build a factory to keep themselves busy.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because it's-- it looked like this is what they were trying to do already this late in the game.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We came in there, and it wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I did not work at the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One of my brothers did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was assigned to the kitchen because the chef of the kitchen knew me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he picked me out in the first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Conditions were just like in any concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Food was not enough unless you worked on the kitchen-- in the kitchen or you can help yourself",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, all German.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
